b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2335,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Issues With Mana Circle Unlocking","message":"<div>We have confirmed that the following issues were occurring since <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1624845600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbWhen unlocking a co-ability node, the co-ability&#39;s effects would sometimes not get upgraded.<\/div><div>\\u30fbIn certain instances, the confirmation screen appearing when unlocking a co-ability node would display a lower eldwater cost than the actual consumed amount of eldwater.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhen unlocking a co-ability node without having the required amount of eldwater, a Support Code: 60001 error would sometimes be displayed, taking you back to the title screen.<\/div><div>Note: These issues don&#39;t reduce the amount of eldwater actually consumed when unlocking co-ability nodes.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>These issues have been fixed around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1624869600\\"><\/span>. Please go back to the title screen and start the game again to resolve them.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1624871400,"prev_article_id":"2244","next_article_id":"2284","image_path":"","update_time":1624876185}}}'